,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:38:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9616fa3548e2d961f937134c5675bf9f9116b9e7","tid":1752220,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:42:51.000Z","msg":"今次運動由一開始已經係體制外抗爭<br />\n甚至係要推翻成個體制<br />\n今次係體制內贏左，最多係當bonus <br />\n同我地追求爭取既野仲爭好遠"},{"pid":"7d6de3f7977f3a6f7b88ab9e164ddd28eaa468b1","tid":1752220,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:50:00.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n勿沖昏頭腦"},{"pid":"6ca10937ef0ae39a52684f1cbd9b29c6b0c607fd","tid":1752220,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"時刻警醒"}]}